The paper deals with image restoration and reconstruction, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV). The use of content-level descriptors and non-local patch means (NLPM) method suggests that the paper may also belong to information retrieval (cs.IR) and deep learning (cs.DL) sub-categories. The paper also mentions the use of genetic algorithms, which falls under machine learning (cs.LG) and multimedia (cs.MM) sub-categories.
